@startuml
actor User
participant "cli.file" as CLI
participant "TranscriptionService" as Service
participant "RivaTranscriber" as Transcriber
participant "Riva ASR Server" as Server

User -> CLI: Ejecuta `python src/cli/file.py audio.wav`
CLI -> Service: transcribe_audio_file(path)
Service -> Transcriber: offline_transcribe(audio_data)
Transcriber -> Server: offline_recognize(gRPC request)
Server --> Transcriber: gRPC response
Transcriber --> Service: transcript_text
Service -> Service: format(transcript)
Service -> Service: write(formatted_text)
Service --> CLI: output_path
CLI --> User: Muestra ruta del archivo
@enduml